<i>I'm here.</i>

21
00:02:12,390 --> 00:02:14,680
My Lady, why're you up so early?

22
00:02:15,830 --> 00:02:21,150
I woke up early to dress and groom myself so you won't have to see my haggard appearance.

23
00:02:21,150 --> 00:02:23,230
Haggard?

24
00:02:24,790 --> 00:02:26,900
My Lady, why would you look haggard?

25
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:29,980
My husband, do you not have an idea?

26
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:40,560
You're not supposed to watch when a woman is getting ready.

27
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,430
My husband, you should go and have your breakfast.

28
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:45,500
Go, quickly. Quickly.

29
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:48,430
Go, quickly. Hurry up.

30
00:04:14,210 --> 00:04:16,330
General, you've returned.

31
00:04:17,820 --> 00:04:21,100
What're you doing, Jin'er?

32
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:24,440
A new batch of medicinal herbs has just arrived from the medicine hall. I'm testing them.

33
00:04:25,980 --> 00:04:28,820
Why do you need to test them out?

34
00:04:28,820 --> 00:04:33,630
Jin'er, if you've taken ill, you must let me know.

35
00:04:34,590 --> 00:04:36,590
I'm perfectly fine, why would I be ill?

36
00:04:36,590 --> 00:04:38,650
You're overthinking things, general.

37
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:14,140
General...

38
00:05:14,140 --> 00:05:16,300
It's very late.

39
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:19,600
I think you should go to bed early, Jin'er.

40
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,500
General...

41
00:05:26,110 --> 00:05:28,200
When you're in my arms,

42
00:05:29,380 --> 00:05:32,220
nothing will harm you, Jin'er.

43
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:39,940
It doesn't matter if we're stranded in the darkness

44
00:05:39,940 --> 00:05:44,010
or if we're... Somewhere else.

45
00:05:44,010 --> 00:05:49,030
I will always recognise you, Jin'er. And I will always find you.

46
00:05:50,510 --> 00:05:56,390
It doesn't matter if you're still in the heyday of your youth, or if you've aged gradually.

47
00:05:58,060 --> 00:06:03,370
I will always love you, as long as you're still my Jin'er.

