62
00:07:10,070 --> 00:07:14,340
General. I have figured out who the spy in the Ninth Princess' entourage is.

63
00:07:17,700 --> 00:07:18,710
Who is it?

64
00:07:18,710 --> 00:07:21,180
It seems the Ninth Princess has already had a lover before all this.

65
00:07:21,180 --> 00:07:22,980
I heard that he used to be an imperial bodyguard.

66
00:07:22,980 --> 00:07:26,010
He'd been chased out of the palace a few days ago by His Majesty.

67
00:07:26,010 --> 00:07:27,240
What happened next?

68
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,970
The princess became depressed,

69
00:07:28,970 --> 00:07:30,860
so His Majesty allowed her to leave the palace in order to drive away her cares.

70
00:07:30,860 --> 00:07:33,270
The strange thing is,

71
00:07:33,270 --> 00:07:36,590
going by His Majesty's temper, he should've ordered the beheading of that bodyguard,

72
00:07:36,590 --> 00:07:41,320
but now, not only has he allowed the princess to leave the palace, he's even allowed him to be kept alive.

73
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:48,000
Then again, the Ninth Princess has already been at the manor for quite a few days.

74
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:53,490
She hasn't even made any moves so far, assuming she's here for the sake of her lover.

75
00:07:58,490 --> 00:08:00,380
<i>The general was not telling the truth.</i>

76
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:03,580
<i>Neither are we a harmonious couple.</i>

77
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:08,200
<i>Princess, if you trust me, listen to me and let me make all the arrangements.</i>

78
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,920
So there's actually nothing wrong with my Jin'er!

79
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:18,480
Did... Something happen to Lord Jin?

80
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:23,830
That Jin'er!

81
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:29,980
Not only was she testing me, but she also managed to come up with such an elaborate plan!

82
00:08:31,540 --> 00:08:34,840
She even willing to risk her own life.

83
00:08:40,230 --> 00:08:43,250
Since she came up with this plan within the plan,

84
00:08:43,250 --> 00:08:46,620
now I will pay her back with a game within the game.

85
00:08:56,780 --> 00:08:58,400
Princess?

86
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,750
Princess, what's happened?

87
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:02,480
Who has dared to bully you in the general's manor? Tell me!

88
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:05,350
No one has bullied me.

89
00:09:05,350 --> 00:09:09,620
It... It was the general.

90
00:09:09,620 --> 00:09:13,980
The general mistook Su Chen for an assassin and arrested him.

91
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:16,140
This Chu Xiuming is so muddleheaded!

92
00:09:16,140 --> 00:09:18,910
He didn't even try to clarify the situation before arresting him.

93
00:09:19,790 --> 00:09:22,170
It's all my fault, it's all my fault. I should have made things clear to him.

94
00:09:22,170 --> 00:09:27,730
It's all right. He and I are not fated to be together in this lifetime.

95
00:09:27,730 --> 00:09:30,880
I can only look forward to being with him in the next lifetime.

96
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,770
Please do not say such things.

97
00:09:32,770 --> 00:09:34,140
I'm still here.

98
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:37,680
I'll tell Chu Xiuming to bring Su Chen back.

99
00:09:41,170 --> 00:09:43,220
I'll go and tell him to do it right this instant.

100
00:09:53,470 --> 00:09:57,780
General, you have worked hard. Jin'er is here to encourage you.

101
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:00,960
It's only about noon,

102
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:03,610
and Jin'er has already come here with good wine.

103
00:10:03,610 --> 00:10:05,720
Are you trying to get me drunk,

104
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,430
and make me lose all logical sense?

105
00:10:07,430 --> 00:10:10,010
Do you have any other intentions?

106
00:10:12,420 --> 00:10:14,580
Then I'll be frank!

107
00:10:17,420 --> 00:10:19,120
General, let him go.

108
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:22,320
Let him go? Let who go?

109
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:26,010
General, did you catch an assassin in the Princess's room?

110
00:10:26,010 --> 00:10:27,280
That's right.

111
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:30,240
This person is a horrible criminal! He dared to attack the Princess?

112
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,430
Don't worry, Jin'er.

113
00:10:31,430 --> 00:10:35,330
I, will definitely punish him heavily. I'll kill him today!

114
00:10:35,330 --> 00:10:37,520
You can't kill him!

115
00:10:38,220 --> 00:10:40,430
I can't kill him?

116
00:10:40,430 --> 00:10:42,870
Why can't I?

117
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:45,100
Is he related to you?

118
00:10:47,290 --> 00:10:50,000
He and I...

119
00:10:52,180 --> 00:10:55,100
-Actually-
-Just who is he?

120
00:10:58,250 --> 00:11:02,950
He is... someone who's closely related to us.

121
00:11:05,010 --> 00:11:07,660
Closely related?

122
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:11,470
He wouldn't be some kind of friend to you?

123
00:11:13,350 --> 00:11:16,270
He counts...

124
00:11:17,860 --> 00:11:20,500
He's Ninth Princess's lover, right?

125
00:11:21,670 --> 00:11:24,500
You know everything?

126
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:30,060
Silly Jin'er. Am I that stupid?

127
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:52,180
Lieutenant General!

128
00:11:52,180 --> 00:11:53,620
Rou Rou.

129
00:11:54,930 --> 00:11:58,720
What terminal illness does Her Ladyship have? You must tell me the truth.

130
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:03,420
Lieutenant General. Why are your words so mean?

131
00:12:03,420 --> 00:12:06,940
You dare to curse Her Ladyship with having a terminal illness? Her body is just fine.

132
00:12:06,940 --> 00:12:09,440
She's healthy and will live a long life!

133
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:12,520
Even General knows about this now. You don't need to keep it a secret.

134
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:15,700
Stop talking nonsense. I think you're the one who's sick.

135
00:12:15,700 --> 00:12:17,280
Our Miss isn't sick!

136
00:12:17,280 --> 00:12:18,530
I-!

137
00:12:18,550 --> 00:12:22,160
If you don't believe me, come to the physicians' office with me. We just need to ask!

138
00:12:26,660 --> 00:12:30,950
Since you also want to help Ninth Princess, then please listen to my plan.

139
00:12:30,950 --> 00:12:32,810
Let's hear it.

140
00:12:32,810 --> 00:12:34,980
Then I will explain it simply.

141
00:12:34,980 --> 00:12:37,020
If there is anything you don't understand,

142
00:12:37,020 --> 00:12:39,650
you can interrupt with questions!

143
00:12:39,650 --> 00:12:41,850
Isn't it just asking for money,

144
00:12:41,850 --> 00:12:44,330
pretending to die, and then running away?

145
00:12:44,330 --> 00:12:46,410
Why wouldn't I understand?

146
00:12:47,790 --> 00:12:49,700
R-r-right.

147
00:12:49,710 --> 00:12:51,900
You could put it that way.

148
00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:53,920
General, how did you know?

149
00:12:53,920 --> 00:13:00,430
Jin'er, your plan is indeed quite...

150
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:02,560
quite...well thought out.

151
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:03,840
Of course!

152
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:07,020
My plan is called tricking the whole world without a single weakness!

153
00:13:08,190 --> 00:13:11,220
If the princess pretends to die of an illness, what will we do about the body?

154
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:14,450
After the forensic expert examines the body, we will bury her!

155
00:13:14,450 --> 00:13:16,440
Oh...and then?

156
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:18,300
In the graveyard,

157
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:21,620
we will make preparations to dig the princess out at any time!

158
00:13:21,620 --> 00:13:27,480
Then what if the Emperor wants to take the princess's body back to the capital, to bury in the royal mausoleum?

159
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:30,010
How will you deal with that?

160
00:13:34,890 --> 00:13:38,290
General...what should we do?

161
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:44,500
Don't panic, Jin'er. I'm here.

162
00:13:45,110 --> 00:13:47,140
General, you have an idea?

163
00:13:49,690 --> 00:13:52,880
Cut it out! Tell me!

164
00:13:56,190 --> 00:14:01,240
We have to wait until the Chongyang Festival to do this.

165
00:14:01,890 --> 00:14:03,870
How far away is the Chongyang Festival?

166
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:07,410
Then don't they still have to painfully wait for some time?

167
00:14:07,410 --> 00:14:08,940
What's so hard about that?

168
00:14:08,940 --> 00:14:13,790
Besides, this is your best acting!

169
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:16,300
My best acting?

170
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:20,670
If the Ninth Princess elopes, there must be no clues left behind,

171
00:14:20,670 --> 00:14:24,740
with no news at all so that there won't be any grounds for people to talk about it.

172
00:14:34,050 --> 00:14:38,090
Physician Li! What's wrong with Her Ladyship?

173
00:14:38,090 --> 00:14:40,460
Her Ladyship indeed does not have a terminal illness.

174
00:14:40,460 --> 00:14:42,350
Look! Didn't I tell you?

175
00:14:42,350 --> 00:14:43,760
However...

176
00:14:43,760 --> 00:14:46,500
However what? She really is sick, right?

177
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:48,850
Her Ladyship is not seriously sick,

178
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:51,750
but...her menstrual cycles are  irregular.

179
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:53,210
Didn't I tell you-?

180
00:14:53,210 --> 00:14:56,250
Then...what does "irregular menstrual cycles" mean?

181
00:14:56,250 --> 00:14:57,990
Nonsense!

182
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:05,880
What happened? Why are you panicking?

183
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:08,340
General! I have something to report!

184
00:15:08,340 --> 00:15:09,930
Tell me.

185
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:15,230
There's one good news and one bad news. What do you want to hear first?

186
00:15:16,010 --> 00:15:17,850
Good news.

187
00:15:18,820 --> 00:15:21,110
Her Ladyship's life isn't in danger.

188
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:22,630
I know.

189
00:15:22,630 --> 00:15:24,410
But-! The Lady-!

190
00:15:24,410 --> 00:15:27,330
The bad news is she's not fully recovered yet! There's still lingering effects!

191
00:15:27,330 --> 00:15:29,420
It's just a woman's disease.

192
00:15:29,420 --> 00:15:32,300
Can illnesses be separated by gender?

193
00:15:32,300 --> 00:15:34,410
No no no. We must find the best physician!

194
00:15:34,410 --> 00:15:36,530
No matter what the price is, we must cure Her Ladyship!

195
00:15:36,530 --> 00:15:40,660
It's fine. She just needs to drink more hot water.

196
00:15:40,660 --> 00:15:43,800
General! How could you be like this?

197
00:15:44,470 --> 00:15:46,830
After going through this obstacle, Her Ladyship was lucky not to die!

198
00:15:46,830 --> 00:15:48,530
It is the heaven's blessing on you!

199
00:15:48,530 --> 00:15:51,420
It is also a chance for you to have supreme enlightenment

200
00:15:51,420 --> 00:15:53,220
on how important and precious Madam is.

201
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:56,000
General, you will know clearly.

202
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:58,160
I know.

203
00:15:59,990 --> 00:16:01,400
Think about it carefully.

204
00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:04,250
If anything happens to Her Ladyship and she dies,

205
00:16:04,250 --> 00:16:07,020
in this world, you'll never see her face again,

206
00:16:07,020 --> 00:16:11,330
you won't hear her voice, and be all alone.

207
00:16:11,330 --> 00:16:13,260
It is such a sad thing!

208
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:22,100
I know.

209
00:16:25,710 --> 00:16:29,600
Life is short. Obtaining true love is already very fortunate.

210
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:33,020
You almost lost Her Ladyship and got her back. You should treasure her more.

211
00:16:33,020 --> 00:16:37,180
You must treat her even better, love her, spoil her, and listen to her!

212
00:16:37,180 --> 00:16:39,170
Do you remember?

213
00:16:42,310 --> 00:16:44,480
I will remember.

214
00:16:47,300 --> 00:16:50,430
If you continue being like this and anger Her Ladyship into running away,

215
00:16:50,430 --> 00:16:53,880
you will find yourself being isolated and with no one to rely on when you are old.

216
00:17:05,670 --> 00:17:09,770
Hey! Starting from today, you must listen to everything Her Ladyship says!

217
00:17:09,770 --> 00:17:13,290
You have to spoil her in food, drink, and clothes, taking good care of her!

218
00:17:14,320 --> 00:17:18,390
Your words make sense. I have some official matters to deal with.

219
00:17:18,390 --> 00:17:20,040
I have to investigate the terrain.

220
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:23,970
In a few days, I will implement this.

221
00:17:29,460 --> 00:17:31,630
Thank you for your reminder.

222
00:17:37,390 --> 00:17:39,620
You have to keep your word!

223
00:17:46,420 --> 00:17:49,240
-Su Su!
-Rou Rou.

224
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:52,440
Look, the moon tonight is so beautiful.

225
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:55,910
Come and enjoy the moon with me.

226
00:17:55,910 --> 00:17:58,020
Su Su, wait a moment for me.

227
00:17:58,020 --> 00:18:01,530
I will bring something to Miss and the General and be right back.

228
00:18:01,530 --> 00:18:03,380
Okay! I'll wait for you.

229
00:18:03,380 --> 00:18:05,100
Wait for me!

230
00:18:16,410 --> 00:18:19,860
General! General!

231
00:18:20,990 --> 00:18:22,620
Gen...

232
00:18:22,620 --> 00:18:24,410
General!

233
00:18:24,410 --> 00:18:26,060
What is it?

234
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:30,350
I...came to bring something to you.

235
00:18:30,350 --> 00:18:32,610
Okay, put it inside.

236
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:41,490
Why are there <i>two</i> Generals?

237
00:18:42,170 --> 00:18:46,120
Did I eat too much? I'm seeing things?

238
00:18:52,760 --> 00:18:55,120
Miss! Miss?

239
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:57,120
You're calling for me?

240
00:18:58,970 --> 00:19:01,420
What's wrong? Did something happen?

241
00:19:04,990 --> 00:19:07,780
A-are you going on a date with the General?

242
00:19:07,780 --> 00:19:09,070
You don't need to care about that.

243
00:19:09,070 --> 00:19:11,240
What's this? It's for me?

244
00:19:11,240 --> 00:19:13,120
Put it inside the room.

245
00:19:21,470 --> 00:19:23,110
This...

246
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:35,520
-Miss!
-You must-

247
00:19:35,520 --> 00:19:37,130
General!

248
00:19:37,130 --> 00:19:40,170
I don't need you here, go and sleep!

249
00:19:41,980 --> 00:19:43,590
Let's go.

250
00:19:55,430 --> 00:19:57,990
General! Miss!

251
00:19:57,990 --> 00:20:01,200
I don't need you here. Go rest.

252
00:20:11,410 --> 00:20:13,890
Am I seeing things?

253
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:17,280
Why are there Misses everywhere?

254
00:20:17,280 --> 00:20:19,770
Why are there Generals everywhere?

255
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:30,130
W-why do you look so pale?

256
00:20:30,130 --> 00:20:33,330
Miss and the General are married!

257
00:20:33,330 --> 00:20:38,080
Suddenly a lot of Misses and Generals appeared!

258
00:20:44,170 --> 00:20:47,520
You don't have a fever. What did you eat?

259
00:20:47,520 --> 00:20:49,660
Did you eat something bad?

260
00:20:50,820 --> 00:20:53,280
I must have eaten too much.

261
00:20:53,280 --> 00:20:56,670
Who cares about that. Let's go enjoy the moon.

262
00:21:15,070 --> 00:21:17,660
If not for Sister Jin and General's brilliant plan,

263
00:21:17,660 --> 00:21:23,420
Su Chen and I, would have to waste tonight's moon.

264
00:21:23,420 --> 00:21:25,830
Don't be so courteous, Ninth Princess.

265
00:21:26,530 --> 00:21:28,730
The Chongyang Festival is tomorrow.

266
00:21:28,730 --> 00:21:32,940
Jin'er and I will make the proper arrangements to help you two leave.

267
00:21:32,940 --> 00:21:34,980
There's no need to worry.

268
00:21:34,980 --> 00:21:37,190
Ninth Princess, don't worry.

269
00:21:37,190 --> 00:21:40,970
General and I are here. There will be no problems.

270
00:21:45,590 --> 00:21:47,660
Thank you for your kindness.

271
00:21:47,660 --> 00:21:52,210
There is no way Su Chen and I can repay what you have done for us.

272
00:21:52,210 --> 00:21:55,730
We are family!  There's no need to be so courteous.

273
00:21:56,500 --> 00:22:01,880
Big Sister, General's move has borne great risk for me.

274
00:22:01,900 --> 00:22:05,730
Su Chen and I are very grateful.

275
00:22:08,590 --> 00:22:12,000
A close family member of mine gave me this makeup pendant.

276
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:15,460
When I was getting ready last time, I saw you liked it.

277
00:22:15,460 --> 00:22:18,760
I will leave with you as a keepsake.

278
00:22:18,760 --> 00:22:21,020
Then I will accept it!

279
00:22:27,930 --> 00:22:30,400
It will be a long journey. Please be careful.

280
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:33,570
Tomorrow, we will use an escape trick that won't be spotted by others

281
00:22:33,570 --> 00:22:35,610
which will eliminate evidence of crime.

282
00:22:50,090 --> 00:22:53,300
<i>[Yong Ning Manor]</i>

283
00:23:24,900 --> 00:23:29,030
General is taking Her Ladyship to enjoy the view during the Chongyang Festival.

284
00:23:29,030 --> 00:23:32,960
What a pair of loving sweethearts.

285
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:35,550
Our Lady is lucky!

286
00:23:35,550 --> 00:23:38,820
However...why is the General bringing Ninth Princess with him?

287
00:23:38,820 --> 00:23:41,390
She's still a princess.

288
00:23:41,390 --> 00:23:44,300
I really hope this princess disappears soon!

289
00:23:44,300 --> 00:23:47,490
Don't get in the way of the General and our Lady!

290
00:23:47,490 --> 00:23:49,240
You want to die?

291
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:50,770
Hurry and go!

292
00:23:55,260 --> 00:23:57,130
Miss Xiao Cong!

293
00:23:57,870 --> 00:23:59,320
Is the General in his library?

294
00:23:59,320 --> 00:24:00,620
No!

295
00:24:00,620 --> 00:24:02,690
Then he's in his own room?

296
00:24:02,690 --> 00:24:03,770
No!

297
00:24:03,770 --> 00:24:05,570
Then do you know where the General went?

298
00:24:05,570 --> 00:24:07,150
I don't know!

299
00:24:07,150 --> 00:24:11,090
Miss Xiao Cong...did I offend you?

300
00:24:11,090 --> 00:24:12,500
Why are you so angry?

301
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:15,490
You offended me in many ways!

302
00:24:16,810 --> 00:24:20,070
Then I will apologize here.

303
00:24:20,700 --> 00:24:23,070
Y-you know what you did wrong?

304
00:24:23,070 --> 00:24:25,610
You're just blindly apologizing.

305
00:24:25,610 --> 00:24:27,200
I don't know.

306
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:30,920
But if you say I was wrong, then I was wrong!

307
00:24:30,920 --> 00:24:33,340
What a fool.

308
00:24:35,710 --> 00:24:39,950
General and Her Ladyship took Ninth Princess up the mountain to enjoy the view!

309
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:43,130
Then do you want to go?

310
00:24:43,130 --> 00:24:45,900
-I will take you there!
-I don't.

311
00:25:10,660 --> 00:25:13,720
The Princess, my wife, and I will go up the mountain to enjoy the view.

312
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:16,900
You all don't need to follow. Just wait here.

313
00:25:16,900 --> 00:25:19,600
I must serve by the Princess's side!

314
00:25:20,430 --> 00:25:23,240
It is a long walk. Your body won't be able to take it.

315
00:25:23,240 --> 00:25:25,400
Instead, you will slow the Princess down.

316
00:25:29,430 --> 00:25:32,280
You. Serve the Princess in her place.

317
00:25:32,280 --> 00:25:33,720
Yes.

318
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:37,930
Princess, Wife, please.

319
00:25:37,930 --> 00:25:39,460
Come.

320
00:26:33,610 --> 00:26:34,980
It's fine now.

321
00:26:34,980 --> 00:26:37,100
We finally got rid of them!

322
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:44,000
Come.

323
00:26:51,140 --> 00:26:54,020
Then let's continue going up.

324
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:19,360
♫ <i> White, tranquil moonlight </i> ♫

325
00:27:19,360 --> 00:27:24,470
♫ <i> Secretly came through the window </i> ♫

326
00:27:24,470 --> 00:27:28,980
♫ <i> Softly laid by my ear </i> ♫

327
00:27:28,980 --> 00:27:34,310
♫ <i> Wandering along with the mind </i> ♫

328
00:27:34,310 --> 00:27:38,710
♫ <i> Gentle, elegant moonlight </i> ♫

329
00:27:38,710 --> 00:27:43,820
♫ <i> Love sparks fly from the fingertips </i> ♫

330
00:27:43,820 --> 00:27:48,460
♫ <i> Worries cause brimming red eyes </i> ♫

331
00:27:48,460 --> 00:27:53,560
♫ <i> Under the stars, tears flow </i> ♫

332
00:27:53,560 --> 00:27:58,790
♫ <i> The cool breeze blows </i> ♫

333
00:27:58,790 --> 00:28:03,480
♫ <i> A light floral scent </i> ♫

334
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:08,190
♫ <i> The aroma overlaps with sorrow </i> ♫

335
00:28:10,840 --> 00:28:13,090
It's time to go.

336
00:28:17,190 --> 00:28:19,020
You've both worked hard.

337
00:28:21,140 --> 00:28:25,040
Once you pass by this mountain, someone will meet you.

338
00:28:27,780 --> 00:28:32,470
♫ <i> Worries ripple through my heart </i> ♫

339
00:28:32,470 --> 00:28:34,280
Have a safe trip.

340
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:48,720
Ninth Princess!

341
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:55,030
I'll miss you. You must be happy!

342
00:28:56,690 --> 00:29:01,760
♫ <i> Secretly came through the window </i> ♫

343
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:06,280
♫ <i> Softly laid by my ear </i> ♫

344
00:29:06,280 --> 00:29:11,050
♫ <i> Wandering along with the mind </i> ♫

345
00:29:27,210 --> 00:29:31,810
Can you...never leave me?

346
00:29:33,250 --> 00:29:34,820
Don't worry, Jin'er.

347
00:29:34,820 --> 00:29:38,280
I will never leave you in this lifetime.

348
00:29:39,420 --> 00:29:42,620
♫ <i> The wind speaks like you </i> ♫

349
00:29:44,100 --> 00:29:45,820
That's right, Jin'er.

350
00:29:46,890 --> 00:29:49,020
Look at this.

351
00:29:49,900 --> 00:29:52,680
This jade hairpin is...?

352
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:54,370
Ninth Princess gave it to me.

353
00:29:54,370 --> 00:29:56,990
She said I originally won this for JIn'er.

354
00:29:56,990 --> 00:30:00,680
♫ <i> Willing to trade a lifetime of prosperity for life's highs and lows </i> ♫

355
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:05,340
♫ <i> Let a bottle of wine seal the story </i> ♫

356
00:30:05,340 --> 00:30:09,920
I really hope those two can be safe.

357
00:30:11,790 --> 00:30:15,460
♫ <i> Flowers bloom and fall, leaving an impression </i> ♫

358
00:30:15,460 --> 00:30:22,880
♫ <i> Naively letting the years pass for one person </i> ♫

359
00:30:22,880 --> 00:30:27,390
♫ <i> Love is the spring to a lifeless land </i> ♫

360
00:30:28,010 --> 00:30:29,870
Your Majesty!

361
00:30:30,990 --> 00:30:32,880
-Your Majesty!
-What is it?

362
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:35,600
-You can both leave.
-Yes.

363
00:30:38,060 --> 00:30:40,230
Reporting to Your Majesty.

364
00:30:40,230 --> 00:30:42,030
News just came from outside the palace.

365
00:30:42,030 --> 00:30:44,660
Ninth Princess went up the mountain to enjoy the view for the Chongyang Festival,

366
00:30:44,660 --> 00:30:46,500
accidentally slipped and fell down the cliff.

367
00:30:46,500 --> 00:30:50,470
The Ninth Princess...is dead!

368
00:30:51,450 --> 00:30:53,020
What?!

369
00:30:54,390 --> 00:30:56,920
Jiu'er is dead?

370
00:31:07,670 --> 00:31:12,180
Do not make a fuss about this. Deal with it quietly.

371
00:31:12,180 --> 00:31:13,890
Yes.

372
00:31:26,110 --> 00:31:28,000
Jiu'er.

373
00:31:30,190 --> 00:31:33,540
I hope you did as I imagined,

374
00:31:33,540 --> 00:31:36,040
and will continue living happily.

375
00:31:42,930 --> 00:31:47,500
<i>[Yong Ning Manor[</i>

376
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:54,920
Ninth Princess can be together with her lover forever!

377
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:56,540
That's such a happy thing!

378
00:31:56,540 --> 00:32:01,590
I hope they can be happy together forever. That way, our efforts won't have been in vain.

379
00:32:02,710 --> 00:32:07,360
As her big sister, I helped her fulfill her wish.

380
00:32:07,360 --> 00:32:09,340
Thankfully, Chu Xiuming trusts me a lot.

381
00:32:09,340 --> 00:32:12,580
He didn't get angry at me for keeping secrets.

382
00:32:12,580 --> 00:32:15,280
I should give him a reward!

383
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:17,580
How are you going to reward me?

384
00:32:17,580 --> 00:32:21,300
Why are you eavesdropping on me like a thief?

385
00:32:21,300 --> 00:32:23,190
I didn't eavesdrop.

386
00:32:23,190 --> 00:32:25,410
You were talking to yourself.

387
00:32:25,410 --> 00:32:27,480
You didn't even notice when I came inside.

388
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:28,910
Thankfully, it was me.

389
00:32:28,910 --> 00:32:32,550
If a thief came inside, that would be dangerous!

390
00:32:32,550 --> 00:32:35,780
I have you to protect me! Why should I be afraid of a thief?

391
00:32:35,780 --> 00:32:38,300
I just have to protect myself against you!

392
00:32:39,810 --> 00:32:43,560
Now that you mention it, you must discuss everything with me in the future!

393
00:32:43,580 --> 00:32:47,480
I am your husband! I will definitely fully support you.

394
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:49,930
Then that depends on your performance!

395
00:32:49,930 --> 00:32:53,940
If you make me happy, I will tell you everything.

396
00:32:53,940 --> 00:32:58,270
If you make me angry, I will keep you outside the door!

397
00:32:58,270 --> 00:33:01,070
If you keep me outside the door for no reason,

398
00:33:01,070 --> 00:33:02,660
you're not afraid I'll run away?

399
00:33:02,660 --> 00:33:05,090
You dare to run away? Then I'll order people to capture you back!

400
00:33:05,090 --> 00:33:07,500
I'll treat you like a servant!

401
00:33:09,270 --> 00:33:13,380
Don't worry, Wife. I won't be a runaway soldier.

402
00:33:14,070 --> 00:33:16,610
But I am willing to be your servant.

403
00:33:28,120 --> 00:33:32,290
Today, allow me to help you put on makeup.

404
00:33:32,290 --> 00:33:35,810
Please be merciful on me in the future.

405
00:33:37,820 --> 00:33:40,840
♫ <i> I pause within my dream </i> ♫

406
00:33:40,840 --> 00:33:42,740
♫ <i> Counting the years of memories </i> ♫

407
00:33:42,740 --> 00:33:47,400
All I want in this lifetime is to draw my wife's eyebrows and apply <i>yellow powder</i> to her forehead.

408
00:33:47,400 --> 00:33:50,550
<i>(A yellow cosmetic powder most likely derived from massicot)</i>

409
00:33:54,210 --> 00:33:56,610
My wife is indeed a beauty.

410
00:33:56,610 --> 00:34:00,790
My heart is entirely captured by you.

411
00:34:02,670 --> 00:34:06,270
♫ <i> Flowers bloom and fall, leaving an impression </i> ♫

412
00:34:07,790 --> 00:34:10,280
Then let's use the makeup pendant from Ninth Princess

413
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:13,740
to put makeup on your wife.

414
00:34:13,740 --> 00:34:17,470
♫ <i> Love is the spring to a lifeless land </i> ♫

415
00:34:17,470 --> 00:34:21,500
♫ <i> Opening the door to my heart without sound or notice </i> ♫

416
00:34:21,500 --> 00:34:25,670
Ninth Princess says this was gifted by her closest family member.

417
00:34:38,250 --> 00:34:42,710
<i>Ninth Princess's close family member? Could it be?</i>

418
00:34:42,710 --> 00:34:44,380
Let me borrow this!

419
00:34:46,230 --> 00:34:48,820
Chu Xiuming! Where are you going?

420
00:35:38,940 --> 00:35:41,850
<i>Could it have been made by the same person?</i>

421
00:35:41,850 --> 00:35:44,410
"My eyes have become dry from gazing into the distance so intently, but all I see are distant mountains and remote rivers." 
 <i> ('Two Lovers Pining' 《两相思》 by the Song dynasty poet)</i>

422
00:35:44,410 --> 00:35:47,640
"How many among the hollow interior are my true confidants?"

423
00:35:47,640 --> 00:35:51,210
<i>(Li Ou/Yu (李禺) is a palindrome. The characters in the second line have been changed – they are not part of the original poem.)</i>

424
00:35:51,210 --> 00:35:54,920
"My eyes have become dry from gazing into the distance so intently, but all I see are distant mountains and remote rivers."

425
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:58,920
"How many among the hollow interior are my true confidants?"

426
00:35:59,710 --> 00:36:01,390
The hollow interior!

427
00:36:15,580 --> 00:36:20,000
My Lord. We have searched the entire mountain, but we didn't find Ninth Princess's body.

428
00:36:20,520 --> 00:36:25,090
My Lord! I stayed by Ninth Princess the entire time and kept an eye on the General's manor just as you ordered,

429
00:36:25,090 --> 00:36:27,460
but that day, General Chu wouldn't let me accompany her!

430
00:36:27,460 --> 00:36:30,220
There was nothing I could do!

431
00:36:30,220 --> 00:36:33,480
Did you discover anything in the General's manor?

432
00:36:33,480 --> 00:36:37,910
Security is tight in the manor. I could not walk around as I wanted.

433
00:36:39,300 --> 00:36:40,570
Take her away and deal with her.

434
00:36:40,570 --> 00:36:41,940
Yes!

435
00:36:42,500 --> 00:36:44,630
My Lord! My Lord, spare me!

436
00:36:44,630 --> 00:36:47,420
My Lord! My Lord, spare me!

437
00:36:48,980 --> 00:36:52,890
The Emperor isn't investigating Ninth Princess's death,

438
00:36:52,890 --> 00:36:55,880
nor is he punishing Chu Xiuming.

439
00:36:57,620 --> 00:37:00,460
Since it's like this,

440
00:37:00,460 --> 00:37:04,550
tomorrow, I will put forward a petition!

441
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:16,990
This seems to be a Falcon Tribe herb.

442
00:37:16,990 --> 00:37:18,570
Herb?

443
00:37:20,810 --> 00:37:22,530
I will go and investigate it for you.

444
00:37:22,530 --> 00:37:24,010
There's no need.

445
00:37:24,660 --> 00:37:26,800
I will do this myself.

446
00:37:48,570 --> 00:37:50,200
Jin'er.

447
00:37:50,200 --> 00:37:54,050
There's something I need to discuss with you.

448
00:37:55,410 --> 00:38:00,670
What is it? It's made you so worried.

449
00:38:02,150 --> 00:38:06,820
The poets have said that not meeting for one day is like three years.

450
00:38:07,310 --> 00:38:10,500
I've always considered it as pretentious and fake.

451
00:38:10,500 --> 00:38:13,780
Only now that I have you by my side,

452
00:38:13,780 --> 00:38:16,160
do I know that their words are true.

453
00:38:17,500 --> 00:38:19,600
Why do you say that?

454
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:26,670
I have long become the devoted lover from those poems.

455
00:38:26,670 --> 00:38:29,340
Every year, every day, and every night, I only want to see my Jin'er,

456
00:38:29,340 --> 00:38:34,220
see my Jin'er, protect my Jin'er, stay by my Jin'er.

457
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:36,640
I cannot bear to be separated from my Jin'er.

458
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:39,470
I can't bear to be separated from you either.

459
00:38:54,410 --> 00:38:58,610
But...there is something important I have to do.

460
00:38:58,610 --> 00:39:03,120
I might have to be away for a while. I've come to say goodbye.

461
00:39:04,150 --> 00:39:06,560
I can't be to let you go!

462
00:39:06,560 --> 00:39:09,950
I'll miss you every day, every week!

463
00:39:11,060 --> 00:39:13,330
Why don't you take me with you?

464
00:39:13,330 --> 00:39:16,120
I definitely won't get in your way!

465
00:39:16,550 --> 00:39:18,600
But I have to go to Falcon Tribe territory.

466
00:39:18,600 --> 00:39:21,640
Bringing you along might not be convenient.

467
00:39:21,640 --> 00:39:24,820
I have important matters to deal with. i don't have the time to play with you.

468
00:39:24,820 --> 00:39:27,410
That's fine. You will deal with your matters.

469
00:39:27,410 --> 00:39:30,260
I will take Rou Rou and play on my own!

470
00:39:32,110 --> 00:39:34,150
But I'm still uneasy.

471
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:38,420
How about this? Have Lieutenant General Xiuyuan protect you two.

472
00:39:38,970 --> 00:39:42,330
Then once you're finished, come and find us!

473
00:39:42,330 --> 00:39:43,900
Okay!

474
00:40:05,790 --> 00:40:08,280
便宜卖了 便宜卖了啊

475
00:40:12,740 --> 00:40:14,070
慢走啊

476
00:40:14,070 --> 00:40:15,610
You must take good care of Her Ladyship.

477
00:40:15,610 --> 00:40:18,950
Don't worry, General. I won't let anything happen to Her Ladyship.

478
00:40:18,950 --> 00:40:22,610
Don't worry! With them here, I'll be fine!

479
00:40:22,610 --> 00:40:25,670
I'm afraid you'll have so much fun, you'll forget about me!

480
00:40:25,670 --> 00:40:30,000
You must not get so caught up in official matters that you'll forget me!

481
00:40:30,550 --> 00:40:33,720
Then I will go take care of my matters. Let's meet up at the inn once we're finished.

482
00:40:33,720 --> 00:40:36,970
Okay! Hurry and go!

483
00:40:47,130 --> 00:40:48,510
Look at this! Look at this! 
 - 包子

484
00:40:48,510 --> 00:40:50,010
热气腾腾的包子

485
00:40:50,010 --> 00:40:52,000
Why don't you buy two?

486
00:40:53,490 --> 00:40:56,840
-There's little sheep too!
-Little sheep!

487
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:58,410
Take a look!

488
00:40:59,600 --> 00:41:01,410
How pretty!

489
00:41:01,410 --> 00:41:03,000
Miss!

490
00:41:05,710 --> 00:41:08,660
This is so unique! I've never seen this before.

491
00:41:08,660 --> 00:41:11,550
Look at this! It's so well made!

492
00:41:11,550 --> 00:41:14,650
There's this too! Does it match my clothes?

493
00:41:14,650 --> 00:41:16,850
-Let me try it on!
-Does this look good?

494
00:41:16,850 --> 00:41:18,550
Let him see it!

495
00:41:18,550 --> 00:41:21,510
Xiuyuan, do I or Rou Rou look better?

496
00:41:24,070 --> 00:41:25,620
My Lady looks good no matter what you wear!

497
00:41:25,620 --> 00:41:27,780
